feat.value: A parallel witness to this document is MONB.GL 63 1.24-70 1.27 (not published by Coptic SCRIPTORIUM). This document is the last fragment in MONB.XJ for the work I See Your Eagerness. A lacuna of 8 pages (4 folios) in XJ follows. A parallel witness to the lacuna appears in codex MONB.GL and contains the end of I See Your Eagerness.
